title: O Neill underlines her support for the farming community at Ploughing Championships (Northern Ireland Executive) ...
text: ( Source : Northern Ireland Executive ) Agriculture and Rural Development Minister Michelle O'Neill today told farmers that she remains determined to do all she can during these challenging times for the agri-food industry. ~ Tuesday, 13
